Hi Dave, 

I was asked to hold off communication until you and Rick decided on next steps. I heard about the request to stay on as 1099 and I fully support it. My ask to Derek was to define what that cadence looks like from a sales leadership perspective so you and Rick have that cadence. I say Rick because I am no longer in a sales leadership role. My sales managerial role was interim with Jim leaving right when I started, so I leaned in to that role. 

It was decided that the Sales Manager responsibility was conflicting with what I was hired to do which requires more attention. Therefore, I no longer share with Rick the responsibility to lead sales calls or ongoing communication with reps. Rick is my sales leader now too. I have two focuses: 1) tech stack, launching marketing, all things digital and 2) being a seller within the system I‚Äôm building. 

You did not hear this announcement which came out yesterday. And like I mentioned, I was also asked to not engage until I heard for sure what Rick decided as that is officially his call with Derek
